orld-europe-66225691.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66225691.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224%20terrorists%20killed%20in%20encounter%20in%20J%26K's%20Poonch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689653365000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101844870%2Cimgsize-47432.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fjk-4-terrorists-killed-in-encounter-with-security-forces-in-poonch%2Farticleshow%2F101844254.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%8BAccording%20to%20Indian%20Army%20officials%2C%20the%20first%20engagement%20between%20security%20forces%20took%20place%20around%2011.30pm%20on%20Monday%20after%20which%20drones%20were%20deployed%20along%20with%20other%20night%20surveillance%20equipment.%20The%20terrorists%20killed%20in%20the%20operation%20are%20most%20likely%20foreign%20terrorists%2C%20said%20Indian%20Army%20officials%2C%20adding%20that%20their%20identities%20are%20being%20ascertained.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Biased%5C%22%20Probe%20Panel%20Trying%20To%20Protect%20Brij%20Bhushan%2C%20Allege%20Wrestlers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20wrestlers%20have%20questioned%20the%20intent%20of%20the%20oversight%20panel%20that%20probed%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20accusations%20against%20WFI%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20and%20alleged%20that%20it%20was%20biased%20towards%20him%2C%20said%20the%20charge-sheet%20filed%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20in%20the%20sensational%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outgoing%20WFI%20chief%20is%20scheduled%20to%20appear%20before%20a%20trial%20court%20today%20in%20pursuance%20of%20summons%20issued%20against%20him%20and%20the%20Federation's%20Assistant%20Secretary%20Vinod%20Tomar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government-formed%20six-member%20panel%2C%20led%20by%20the%20legendary%20Indian%20boxer%20MC%20Mary%20Kom%2C%20had%20submitted%20its%20report%20to%20the%20government%20but%20it%20was%20not%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainants%2C%20in%20their%20separate%20statements%2C%20alleged%20that%20the%20panel%20appeared%20biased%20towards%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20BJP%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charge-sheet%20that%20runs%20into%201599%20pages%2C%20contained%20statements%20of%2044%20witnesses%2C%20besides%20six%20statements%20by%20the%20complainants%20which%20were%20recorded%20under%20CrPC%20164.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20after%20giving%20my%20statement%20before%20the%20(oversight)%20committee%20whenever%20I%20visited%20the%20Federation%20office%2C%20the%20accused%20looked%20at%20me%20with%20distasteful%20and%20lustful%20eyes%20and%20made%20wrong%20gestures%20which%20made%20me%20feel%20insecure%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20of%20the%20complainants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20the%20video%20recording%20was%20being%20switched%20off%20and%20on%20while%20I%20was%20giving%20my%20statement%20and%20in%20spite%20of%20my%20request%20the%20committee%20did%20not%20supply%20me%20a%20copy%20of%20my%20video%20recording.%20I%20fear%20that%20my%20statement%20may%20not%20have%20been%20recorded%20in%20entirety%20and%20may%20also%20have%20been%20tampered%20with%20to%20protect%20the%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20of%20the%20wrestler%20read%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20complainant%20said%20that%20she%20was%20made%20a%20part%20of%20the%20WFI%20sexual%20harassment%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20such%20cases%20without%20her%20consent.%20All%20national%20sports%20federations%20are%20supposed%20to%20have%20Internal%20Complaints%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20never%20issued%20any%20formal%20communication%20informing%20me%20about%20such%20approval%2C%20nor%20was%20any%20formal%20communication%20was%20received%20by%20me%20seeking%20my%20approval%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20committee%20of%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20accused%2C%20in%20conspiracy%20with%20accused%20No.%202%20and%20other%20unknown%20persons%2C%20has%20deliberately%20done%20this%20to%20suppress%20my%20voice%20and%20allegations%20against%20him.%20He%20has%2C%20without%20my%20approval%20or%20consensus%2C%20made%20me%20part%20of%20the%20said%20committee%20and%20is%20now%20alleging%20that%20in%20spite%20of%20being%20part%20of%20the%20committee%2C%20I%20am%20falsely%20alleging%20to%20be%20a%20victim%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20complainant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20'victim'%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20oversight%20panel%20did%20not%20provide%20her%20the%20recording%20when%20demanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20serious%20doubts%20that%20that%20my%20statement%20on%20video%20may%20not%20have%20been%20recorded%20in%20entirety%20or%20may%20have%20been%20altered%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20protect%20the%20accused%20and%20thus%20I%20requested%20for%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20video%20recording.%20However%20members%20of%20the%20oversight%20committee%20flatly%20turned%20down%20my%20request.%26quot%3B%20Delhi%20police%20had%20justified%20not%20arresting%20the%20accused%2C%20saying%20both%20Singh%20and%20WFI%20Assistant%20Secretary%20Tomar%20complied%20with%20the%20law%20by%20joining%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BResults%20of%20digital%2Felectronic%20devices%20and%20exhibits%20seized%20and%20deposited%20with%20the%20concerned%20Forensic%20Labs%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20received%20and%20shall%20be%20filed%20through%20supplementary%20police%20reports.%20The%20analysis%20of%20requisitioned%20CDRs%20etc.%2C%20as%20found%20appropriate%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20prosecution%20shall%20also%20be%20submitted%20expeditiously%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said%20in%20the%20charge-sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20th