20more%20likely%20be%20around%20Aus%247%20billion%2C%20which%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bwell%20and%20truly%20too%20much%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20difficult%20calls%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20very%20difficult%20decisions%20in%20this%20job.%20This%20is%20not%20one%20of%20them.%20Frankly%2C%20%247%20billion%20for%20a%20sporting%20event%2C%20we%20are%20not%20doing%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Melbourne.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20take%20money%20out%20of%20hospitals%20and%20schools%20to%20host%20an%20event%20that%20is%20three%20times%20the%20cost%20estimated%20and%20budgeted%20for%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Games%20will%20not%20proceed%20in%20Victoria%20in%202026.%20We%20have%20informed%20Commonwealth%20Games%20authorities%20of%20our%20decision%20to%20seek%20to%20terminate%20the%20contract%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20--%20featuring%2020%20sports%20and%2026%20disciplines%20--%20was%20due%20to%20be%20held%20across%20five%20regional%20hubs%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20Geelong%2C%20Ballarat%2C%20Bendigo%2C%20Gippsland%20and%20Shepparton%2C%20with%20each%20having%20its%20own%20athletes'%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndrews%20said%20his%20team%20had%20looked%20at%20cutting%20the%20number%20of%20hubs%20or%20even%20moving%20the%20Games%20to%20the%20Victoria%20state%20capital%20Melbourne%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bnone%20of%20those%20options%20stack%20up%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20announced%20a%20Aus%242%20billion%20support%20package%20for%20regional%20Victoria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndrews%20refused%20to%20say%20how%20much%20it%20was%20costing%20to%20terminate%20the%20agreement%2C%20but%20insisted%20talks%20with%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%20Federation%20were%20amicable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Federation%20was%20not%20happy%2C%20blasting%20the%20move%20as%20%26quot%3Bhugely%20disappointing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20disappointed%20that%20we%20were%20only%20given%20eight%20hours'%20notice%20and%20that%20no%20consideration%20was%20given%20to%20discussing%20the%20situation%20to%20jointly%20find%20solutions%20prior%20to%20this%20decision%20being%20reached%20by%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESolution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVictoria%20was%20only%20awarded%20the%20contract%2014%20months%20ago%20as%20the%20exclusive%20bidder%2C%20with%20the%20Federation%20claiming%20the%20state%20had%20since%20decided%20to%20include%20more%20sports%2C%20added%20an%20additional%20regional%20hub%2C%20and%20changed%20plans%20for%20venues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20additional%20expense%20was%20%26quot%3Boften%20against%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%20Federation%20and%20Commonwealth%20Games%20Australia%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20had%20received%20assurances%20that%20%26quot%3Bsufficient%20funding%20was%20available%20to%20deliver%20the%20Victoria%202026%20Commonwealth%20Games%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20pull%20out%20leaves%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20Games%20up%20in%20the%20air%2C%20with%20fewer%20and%20fewer%20countries%20showing%20interest%20in%20recent%20times%20to%20take%20on%20a%20spectacle%20seen%20as%20losing%20its%20relevance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Federation%20insisted%20it%20remained%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20finding%20a%20solution%20for%20the%20Games%20in%202026%20that%20is%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20our%20athletes%20and%20the%20wider%20Commonwealth%20Sport%20Movement%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20typically%20attracts%20more%20than%204%2C000%20athletes%20from%20the%2054%20nations%20of%20the%20Commonwealth%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20which%20are%20former%20territories%20of%20the%20British%20Empire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20Games%2C%20in%202022%2C%20were%20held%20in%20England