2Fcricket%2Findia-in-west-indies%2Fchief-selector-ajit-agarkar-to-meet-rahul-dravid-rohit-sharma-in-west-indies-for-world-cup-road-map%2Farticleshow%2F101843289.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDA's%2038%20vs%20Opposition's%2026%3A%20Battle%20Of%20Alliances%20Today%20Ahead%20Of%202024%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%2026%20opposition%20leaders%20who%20met%20in%20Bengaluru%20yesterday%2C%20finalised%20the%20agenda%20for%20today's%20talks.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20former%20UPA%20chairperson%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20is%20set%20to%20be%20named%20as%20the%20President%20of%20the%20Front%2C%20with%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20as%20the%20Convenor.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAt%20BJP's%20grand%20show%20of%20strength%20in%20Delhi%2C%20a%20parallel%20event%20to%20the%20opposition's%20unity%20meet%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%2038%20parties%20have%20been%20invited%20to%20attend%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20NDA%20meet%20may%20be%20attended%20by%20several%20new%20allies%2C%20including%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20led%20by%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20the%20NCP%20faction%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar.%20Others%20such%20as%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20leader%20Chirag%20Paswan%20could%20also%20attend%20the%20mega%20meet.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20Bengaluru%2C%20besides%20Mrs%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20opposition%20meet%20is%20being%20attended%20by%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Chief%20Ministers%20MK%20Stalin%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20and%20RJD%20Chief%20Lalu%20Prasad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BLike-minded%20opposition%20parties%20shall%20closely%20work%20together%20to%20foster%20an%20agenda%20of%20social%20justice%2C%20inclusive%20development%20and%20national%20welfare.%20We%20want%20to%20free%20the%20people%20of%20India%20from%20the%20autocratic%20and%20anti-people%20politics%20of%20hate%2C%20division%2C%20economic%20inequality%20and%20loot...%20United%20We%20Stand%2C%20for%20this%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kharge.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBJP%20President%20JP%20Nadda%20alleged%20that%20opposition%20leaders%20are%20uniting%20for%20selfish%20reasons%2C%20in%20order%20to%20shield%20themselves%20from%20corruption%20charges%20worth%20over%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20crore.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20'bhanumati%20ka%20kunba'%20(motley%20group)%2C%20an%20opportunistic%20alliance.%20It%20has%20no%20agenda%2C%20commitment%20and%20vision.%20Their%20only%20aim%20is%20to%20grab%20power%20and%20serve%20their%20own%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadda%20said%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20opposition%20parties%20have%20been%20requested%20to%20suggest%20a%20name%20for%20their%20united%20front%20that%20includes%20the%20word%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B.%20The%20tagline%20for%20it%20will%20be%20%26quot%3BUnited%20We%20Stand%26quot%3B.%20Suggestions%20have%20also%20been%20sought%20for%20the%20Common%20Minimum%20Programme%2C%20but%20the%20subject%20of%20states%20will%20be%20kept%20separate.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENCP%20patriarch%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Janata%20Dal-Secular%20(JDS)%20leader%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20opposition%20meeting.%20Although%20Mr%20Pawar%20is%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Bengaluru%20for%20the%20second%20day%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20will%20attend%20the%20meeting%20or%20not.%20%26quot%3BAll%20parties%20having%20the%20will%20and%20guts%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP%20are%20welcome%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Congress%20leader%20Pawan%20Khera.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%2C%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%2C%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy's%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20and%20Shiromani%20A