he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Ray%20still%20thinks%20that%C2%A0the%20most%20charming%20parts%20of%20the%20house%20are%20the%20window%20sills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20walls%20are%20two%20and%20a%20half%20feet%20thick%2C%20so%20all%20the%20window%20sills%20are%20that%20deep%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20creates%20a%20really%20beautiful%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20couple's%20completed%20cob%20house%20is%20about%20750%20square%20feet.%20It%20comprises%20a%20600-square-foot%20main%20floor%20and%20a%20150-square-foot%20loft.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221454%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cob%20house%20sits%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20grassy%20field.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ae55228ed31300199e8e2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221090%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20photo%20of%20the%20cob%20house's%20exterior.%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Ray%2FSpiritwood%20Natural%20Building%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20moved%20into%20their%20new%20cob%20house%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202019%20%E2%80%94%20shortly%20after%20Katherine%20gave%20birth%20to%20their%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20bedrooms%20and%20one%20bathroom%20in%20the%20house.%20Ray%20says%20they%20draw%20electricity%20from%20the%20grid%20and%20rely%20on%20a%20well%20on%20the%20property%20for%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20a%20flushing%20toilet%2C%20the%20couple%20uses%20a%20composting%20toilet%20in%20their%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20sawdust%20toilet%2C%26quot%3B%20Ray%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20after%20you%20use%20the%20toilet%2C%20you%20put%20sawdust%20on%20it%2C%20and%20then%20it%20gets%20emptied%20into%20a%20larger%20composting%20area%20we%20have%20on%20the%20property.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOne%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20living%20in%20a%20cob%20house%20is%20that%20the%20interiors%20are%20much%20cooler%20than%20typical%20house