20a%20charter%20vessel%20but%20only%20took%20close%20friends%20on%20trips.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20he%20could%20pay%20his%20own%20company%2C%20report%20losses%2C%20and%20save%20on%20his%20tax%20bill%2C%20per%20ProPublica.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBillionaire%20GOP%20donor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-harlan-crow-clarence-thomas-trips-billionaire-gop-megadonor-2023-4%5C%22%3EHarlan%20Crow's%20lavish%20yacht%20trips%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas%20may%20have%20been%20facilitated%20by%20questionable%20tax%20practices%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrow's%20relationship%20with%20Thomas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclarence-thomas-luxury-vacations-gop-megadonor-harlan-crow-report-says-2023-4%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20scrutinized%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20ProPublica%20reported%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Fclarence-thomas-scotus-undisclosed-luxury-travel-gifts-crow%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20Crow%20funded%20years%20of%20vacations%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Thomas%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenate-committee-asks-harlan-crow-to-list-gifts-given-to-a-justice-2023-5%5C%22%3Ewho%20failed%20to%20disclose%20the%20outings%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20of%20those%20were%20trips%20aboard%20Crow's%20yacht%2C%20the%20Michaela%20Rose%2C%20and%20were%20organized%20through%20Rochelle%20Charter%2C%20a%20company%20registered%20to%20charter%20the%20yacht.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20trips%20on%20the%20yacht%20%E2%80%94%20registered%20as%20a%20charter%20vessel%20%E2%80%94%20were%20actually%20limited%20to%20Crow's%20inner%20circle%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Fharlan-crow-slashed-tax-bill-clarence-thomas-superyacht%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20ProPublica%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Crow%20paid%20his%20own%20company%20for%20private%20trips%20on%20the%20yacht%20and%20was%20able%20to%20secure%20tax%20breaks%20and%20lower%20his%20tax%20bill%2C%20according%20to%20tax%20data%20from%202003%20through%202015%20reviewed%20by%20ProPublica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETax%20experts%20and%20politicians%20who%20spoke%20to%20the%20outlet%20said%20that%20such%20a%20practice%20could%20amount%20to%20gaming%20the%20system%20and%20should%20be%20audited.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20what%20information%20is%20available%2C%20this%20has%20the%20look%20of%20a%20textbook%20billionaire%20tax%20scam%2C%26quot%3B%20Senate%20Finance%20Committee%20Chair%20Ron%20Wyden%20told%20ProPublica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Crow%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20points%20out%20that%20Crow%20recorded%20%248%20million%20in%20losses%20for%20the%20family%20company%20Rochelle%20Charter%2C%20saving%20on%20taxes%20as%20a%20result%20between%202003%20and%202015.%20The%20megadonor%20purported%20to%20charter%20the%20boat%20for%20profit%20and%20instead%20took%20friends%20like%20Thomas%20for%20cruises%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20Crow%20and%20Thomas%20first%20faced%20scrutiny%20related%20to%20the%2020%20years%20worth%20of%20undisclosed%20trips%20Crow%20is%20accused%20of%20gifting%20to%20Thomas%2C%20per%20ProPublica.%20The%20outlet%20later%20reported%20that%20Crow%20purchased%20Thomas'%20mother's%20house%20and%20allowed%20her%20to%20live%20there%20without%20paying%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Thomas%20%E2%80%94%20who%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclarence-thomas-extension-financial-disclosures-supreme-court-2023-6%5C%22%3Easked%20for%20an%20extension%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20file%20his%20financial%20disclosure%20forms%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20said%20that%20at%20the%20time%20he%20wasn't%20aware%20that%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclarence-thomas-harlan-crow-response-trips-supreme-court-ethics-2023-4%5C%22%3Emeant%20to%20disclose%20the%20trips%20with%20Crow.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrow%20claimed%20to%20the%20Dallas%20Morning%20News%20that%20the%20revelations%20about%20his%20relationship%20with%20Thomas%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharlan-crow-clarence-thomas-relationship-propublica-hit-job-2023-4%5C%22%3Ea%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20hit%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECongress%20has%20probed%20Crow's%20and%20Thomas's%20relationship%2C%20asking%20for%20a%20detailed%20disclosure%20of%20the%20gifts%20that%20Crow%20has%20bestowed%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20justices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20stands%2C%20a%20group%20of%20judges%2C%20the%20Committee%20on%20Financial%20Disclosure%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudges-investigating-clarence-thomas-committee-financial-disclosure-2023-5%5C%22%3Eis%20investigating%20Thomas%20and%20disclosure%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20Senate%20Democrats%20have%20mounted%20a%20separate%20attempt%20to%20investigate%20Thomas%20and%20other%20justices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharlan-crow-yacht-trips-justice-clarence-thomas-tax-report-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689644989000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b5db51db90260019355dd3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharlan-crow-yacht-trips-justice-clarence-thomas-tax-report-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Billionaire%20GOP%20donor%20Harlan%20Crow%20was%20accused%20of%20using%20lavish%20yacht%20trips%20with%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas%20to%20save%20on%20taxes%2C%20per%20ProPublica.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22