a%20fundraiser%20project.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b59a15db90260019355573%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22407%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt's%20been%20reported%20that%20naval%20drones%20were%20used%20to%20attack%20the%20Kerch%20Strait%20Bridge.%3Cp%3EUnited%2024%2FUkrainian%20government%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWaterborne%20drones%20are%20an%20inexpensive%20asset%2C%20giving%20Ukraine%20an%20%26quot%3Basymmetric%26quot%3B%20naval%20edge%20against%20Russia.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERussia%20blamed%20Ukraine%20for%20using%20the%20drones%20to%20attack%20the%20Kerch%20Strait%20Bridge%20in%20Crimea%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20bridge%20is%20key%20for%20Russian%20economic%2C%20military%2C%20and%20cultural%20interests%20in%20occupied%20Crimea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20heavily%20relied%20on%20cheap-but-effective%20airborne%20drones%20for%20attacks%20on%20front-line%20Russian%20positions%20and%20on%20targets%20behind%20enemy%20lines.%20Waterborne%20drones%20are%20also%20inexpensive%20and%20devastating%2C%20and%20there%20are%20indications%20they%20were%20used%20to%20damage%20a%20key%20Russian%20bridge%20into%20Crimea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20explosions%20rocked%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F12-mile-bridge-crimea-lifeline-russia-constant-attacks-headache-2023-7%5C%22%3E12-mile%20Kerch%20Strait%20Bridge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20damaging%20the%20roadbed%2C%20halting%20traffic%2C%20and%20killing%20two%20adults.%20Russian%20authorities%20blamed%20Kyiv%2C%20vowing%20%26quot%3Btargeted%20and%20quite%20inhumane%26quot%3B%20repercussions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20at%20least%20the%20second%20time%20the%20bridge%20has%20been%20damaged%20in%20less%20than%20year.%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-attack-on-russia-crimea-bridge-is-blow-to-putin-2022-10%5C%22%20rel%3D%