0naval%20drone%20fleet%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20unmanned%20vessels%20first%20gave%20them%20an%20operational%20advantage%20to%20target%20Russian%20ships%20in%20October%202022.%20%26quot%3BThe%20killers%20of%20Ukrainian%20civilians%20%E2%80%94%20warships%20armed%20with%20missiles%20%E2%80%94%20became%20targets%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20state-run%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fu24.gov.ua%2Fnavaldrones%5C%22%3Efundraiser%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20can%20pack%20a%20punch%2C%20and%20they're%20relatively%20cheap%2C%20too%2C%20especially%20compared%20to%20a%20traditional%20warship%20or%20the%20defenses%20required%20to%20defeat%20these%20unmanned%20surface%20vessels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cost%20of%20manufacturing%20and%20fielding%20these%20vehicles%20is%20considerably%20less%20%E2%80%94%20many%20magnitudes%20less%20%E2%80%94%20than%20the%20cost%20of%20trying%20to%20defend%20against%20them%20and%20just%20basic%20resource%20allocation%20in%20trying%20to%20interdict%20and%20destroy%20these%20assets%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Samuel%20Bendett%2C%20a%20research%20analyst%20with%20the%20Center%20for%20Naval%20Analyses'%20Russia%20Studies%20Program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20again%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20defending%20against%20such%20vehicles%20falls%20on%20the%20defender%20%E2%80%94%20a%20single%20ship%2C%20a%20fleet%2C%20or%20an%20entire%20country%20%E2%80%94%20while%20the%20cost%20of%20manufacturing%20them%20is%20considerably%20smaller.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Basymmetric%20advantage%26quot%3B%20for%20Ukraine.%20They%20stress%20Russian%20defenses%20at%20a%20low%20cost%20to%20the%20Ukrainians%20and%20their%20available%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221881%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20picture%20of%20the%20Kerch%20Bridge%20between%20Russia%20and%20Crimea%20damaged%20by%20explosions%20on%20July%2017%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b57b5e64dab3001999f718%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221043%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20Ukraine%20didn't%20take%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack%2C%20Kyiv%20has%20repeatedly%20threatened%20to%20target%20the%20bridge.%3Cp%3ECrimea24TV%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kerch%20Bridge%2C%20which%20may%20have%20been%20the%20target%20of%20these%20assets%2C%20is%20a%20valuable%20access%20point%20for%20Moscow%2C%20connecting%20Russia%20to%20Crimea%20and%20allowing%20economic%20and%20cultural%20control%20over%20the%20illegally%20occupied%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20served%20as%20an%20ideal%20transportation%20route%20for%20Russia's%20military%20equipment%20before%20its%20February%202022%20invasion.%C2%A0Supply%20routes%20have%20mostly%20shifted%20to%20northern%20land%20bridges%20since%20October's%20attack%2C%20according%20to%20Bendett%2C%20but%20the%20repeated%20incidents%20raise%20a%20host%20of%20questions%20about%20how%20Russia%20is%20going%20to%20%C2%A0defend%20the%20Kerch%20Bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20USVs%20don't%20travel%20for%20thousands%20of%20kilometers%2C%20they%20have%20to%20operate%20in%20relative%20proximity%20to%20their%20operators%20or%20their%20launching%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Bendett%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20defend%20a%20long%20bridge%20like%20that%3F%20Where%20do%20you%20place%20your%20defenses%3F%20Do%20you%20fly%20patrols%20around%20it%3F%20Do%20you%20install%20sensors%20on%20it%20all%20the%20time%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20maritime%20patrols%20all%20the%20time%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20difficult%20to%20properly%20and%20completely%20defend%20an%20asset%20as%20large%20as%20a%20bridge%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20although%20it's%20too%20early%20to%20tell%20how%20significant%20Monday's%20attack%20on%20the%20bridge%20is%20and%20what%20the%20impacts%20will%20be%2C%20especially%20since%20only%20part%