ttributing%20the%20deaths%20to%20other%20reasons%20are%20%E2%80%9Cspeculation%20and%20hearsay%20and%20not%20based%20on%20any%20scientific%20evidence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20state%20government%20on%20July%2017%20transferred%20chief%20wildlife%20warden%20J.S.%20Chauhan%20with%20immediate%20effect%20on%20%E2%80%9Cadministrative%20grounds%E2%80%9D.%20Aseem%20Srivastava%2C%20formerly%20the%20principal%20chief%20conservator%20of%20forest%20(production)%20will%20now%20take%20over%20as%20PCCF%20(Wildlife)%20in%20Chauhan%E2%80%99s%20stead.%20The%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%20met%20on%20July%2017%20and%20discussed%20matters%20including%20the%20recent%20deaths%2C%20forest%20officials%20said.%20According%20to%20them%2C%20daily%20press%20releases%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%20to%20%E2%80%9Cavoid%20confusion%E2%80%9D%20are%20possibly%20on%20the%20cards.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECheetah%20deaths%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProject%20Cheetah%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20cheetah%20introduction%20programme%2C%20is%20unfolding%20in%20the%20grasslands%20of%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Of%20the%2020%20cheetahs%20that%20were%20brought%20in%20from%20Namibia%20and%20South%20Africa%20in%20September%20last%20year%2C%20five%20died%20due%20to%20various%20reasons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%20two%20deaths%20%E2%80%93%20of%20male%20cheetahs%20Tejas%20and%20Surya%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20mired%20in%20controversy.%20Tejas%2C%20which%20died%20on%20July%2011%20in%20its%20enclosure%2C%20had%20a%20wound%20above%20its%20neck%2C%20and%20forest%20officials%20said%20this%20occurred%20after%20a%20violent%20interaction%20with%20a%20female%20cheetah.%20A%20post-mortem%20revealed%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cinternally%20weak%E2%80%9D%20and%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20recover%20from%20%E2%80%9Ctraumatic%20shock%E2%80%9D.%20A%20free-ranging%20male%20Surya%20died%20on%20July%2014%2C%20and%20authorities%20noticed%20a%20wound%20on%20his%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2014%2C%20South%20African%20veterinarian%20Adrian%20Tordiffe%20said%20that%20both%20deaths%20seem%20to%20be%20caused%20by%20moisture%20accumulation%20under%20the%20animal%E2%80%99s%20radio%20collar%20due%20to%20the%20humid%20weather%2C%20which%20caused%20septicaemia%2C%20an%20infection%20of%20the%20bloodstream.%20Rajesh%20Gopal%2C%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%20(which%20oversees%20and%20advises%20Project%20Cheetah%20on%20cheetah%20management)%2C%20confirmed%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20July%2015%20that%20this%20was%20true%20and%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccause%20for%20concern%E2%80%9D.%20All%20cheetahs%20fitted%20with%20radio%20collars%20would%20be%20examined%20and%20their%20detailed%20health%20checks%20done%2C%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAll%20natural%20deaths%2C%20insists%20NTCA%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20all%20deaths%20are%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20(NTCA%2C%20which%20implements%20Project%20Cheetah%20in%20India)%20said%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1939948%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estatement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20next%20day%2C%20July%2016%2C%20after%20the%20publication%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20story%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equoting%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%20members%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Any%20reports%20in%20the%20media%20attributing%20these%20deaths%20to%20other%20reasons%20including%20radio%20collars%20%E2%80%9Care%20not%20based%20on%20any%20scientific%20evidence%20but%20are%20speculation%20and%20hearsay%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CProject%20Cheetah%20is%20yet%20to%20complete%20a%20year%20and%20it%20will%20be%20premature%20to%20conclude%20the%20outcome%20in%20terms%20of%20success%20and%20failure%2C%20since%20Cheetah%20reintroduction%20is%20a%20long-term%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20consultations%20with%20international%20cheetah%20experts%2Fveterinary%20doctors%20from%20South%20Africa%20and%20Namibia%20are%20being%20conducted%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%20to%20investigate%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20cheetah%20deaths.%20Aspects%20including%20existing%20monitoring%20protocols%2C%20managerial%20inputs%2C%20veterinary%20facilities%2C%20training%20and%20capacity-building%20aspects%20are%20being%20reviewed%20by%20independent%20national%20experts%2C%20the%20statement%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20project%20and%20has%20expressed%20satisfaction%20over%20its%20implementation%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETordiffe%2C%20who%20is%20also%20part%20of%20the%20Steering%20Committee%2C%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20has%20raised%20serious%20concerns%20regarding%20cheetah%20management%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Kuno.%20He%20cited%20the%20lack%20of%20veterinary%20care%20available%20to%20the%20cheetahs%2C%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20senior%20scientist%20at%20Kuno%20to%20coordinate%20the%20management%20and%20monitoring%20of%20the%20animals%2C%20as%20concerns%20that%20need%20immediate%20addressing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETordiffe%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Findian-wildlife-authorities-attribute-cheetah-deaths-in-kuno-national-park-to-natural-causes%2Fcid%2F1952520%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20July%2017%20that%20instead%20of%20labeling%20deaths%20as%20natural%20or%20unnatural%2C%20it%20is%20better%20to%20speak%20of%20avoidable%20versus%20unavoidable%20deaths.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20know%20a%20potential%20risk%20and%20do%20nothing%20to%20mitigate%20that%20risk%2C%20then%20it%20is%20an%20avoidable%20risk%20and%20you%20failed%20in%20your%20responsibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20media%20house.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fasia%2Findia%2Fproject-cheetah-africa-kuno-deaths-b2376338.html%3Fr%3D89130%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20currently%2C%20communication%20failure%20with%20the%20Indian%20team%20is%20a%20problem.%20He%20has%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20little%20access%20to%20accurate%2C%20real-time%20data%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20cheetahs%20from%20Kuno.%20He%20added%20that%20poor%20management%20was%20%E2%80%9Calmost%20certainly%E2%80%9D%20a%20factor%20in%20the%20death%20of%20the%20three%20cubs%20born%20to%20the%20cheetah%20named%20Jwala.%20The%20cubs%20died%20within%20days%20of%20each%20other%20in%20May%3B%20currently%2C%20a%20single%20cub%20remains%20in%20Kuno.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMP%20gets%20new%20Chief%20Wildlife%20Warden%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20state%20government%20on%20Monday%20transferred%20the%20Chief%20Wildlife%20Warden%20J.S.%20Chauhan%2C%20currently%20the%20Principal%20Chief%20Conservator%20of%20Forest%2C%20Wildlife%2C%20to%20the%20Production%20wing%2C%20and%20the%20PCCF%2C%20Production%2C%20has%20been%20appointed%20the%20new%20PCCF%20(Wildlife)%2C%20with%20immediate%20effect%20as%20of%20July%2017.%20Aseem%20Srivastava%20will%20be%20the%20new%20Chief%20Wildlife%20Warden.%20As%20per%20the%20government%20order%2C%20the%20transfers%20have%20been%20made%20on%20%E2%80%9Cadministrative%20grounds%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20postings%20are%20temporary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProject%20Cheetah%20was%20kicked%20off%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20during%20Chauhan%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20as%20Chief%20Wildlife%20Warden.%20In%20April%20this%20year%2C%20Chauhan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-govt-asks-ntca-to-find-second-home-for-cheetahs-kuno-unable-to-accommodate-more-than-10-big-cats-mukandara-wildlife-sanctuary-identified-as-potential-site-101681844727775.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econfirmed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20MP%20government%20had%20written%20to%20the%20NTCA%20to%20find%20a%20second%20home%20for%20the%20cheetahs%20since%20Kuno%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20house%20more%20than%2010%20of%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2017%2C%20Chauhan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fafter-kuno-deaths-radio-collars-set-to-be-taken-off-10-cheetahs-8842793%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20infections%20occurring%20in%20the%20cheetahs%20because%20of%20their%20radio%20collars%20during%20the%20monsoon%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20possibility%E2%80%9D%20and%20could%20be%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20reasons%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20cheetah%20deaths.%20He%20had%20also%20suggested%20that%20two%20other%20male%20cheetahs%2C%20Gaurav%20and%20Shaurya%2C%20may%20have%20similar%20problems%20as%20Tejas%20and%20Surya%20did.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDaily%20updates%20on%20Project%20Cheetah%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Steering%20Committee%20meeting%20today%2C%20July%2017%2C%20discussed%20several%20aspects%20including%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%20and%20decisions%20that%20can%20be%20expected%20tomorrow%2C%20Kuno%20divisional%20forest%20officer%20(DFO)%20P.K.%20Verma%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20Monday.%20Orders%20have%20also%20been%20issued%20replacing%20Verma%20with%20immediate%20effect.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NTCA%20and%20the%20government%20of%20India%20would%20also%20be%20issuing%20a%20press%20release%20every%20day%20so%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20confusion%20in%20the%20media%2C%20or%20%E2%80%9Cconflicting%20news%20coming%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20senior%20official%20in%20the%20department%2C%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20said%20that%20not%20all%20cheetahs%20would%20be%20captured%20for%20examination.%20The%20teams%20and%20veterinarians%20on%20the%20ground%20are%20%E2%80%9Cclosely%20watching%E2%80%9D%20the%20cheetahs%2C%20the%20official%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20no%20other%20animals%20had%20collar-related%20injuries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689615081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F01124706%2FFr_KjcBXoAEm2rW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fauthorities-say-recent-cheetah-deaths-due-to-natural-causes-mp-chief-wildlife-warden-transferred%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20has%20said%20any%20reports%20attributing%20the%20deaths%20to%20other%20reasons%20are%20'speculation%20and%20h