%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fajit-pawar-ncp-mlas-hold-second-meeting-with-sharad-pawar-in-24-hours-urge-him-to-keep-party-united%2Farticle67089994.ece%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20meeting%20was%20unplanned%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20was%20unaware%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20faction%20coming%20to%20see%20him.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20the%20Chavan%20Centre%20when%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20other%20MLAs%20came.%20He%20was%20not%20expecting%20them%20today.%20It%20was%20a%20surprise%20visit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-pawar-meets-uncle-sharad-pawar-second-meeting-in-24-hours-4214647%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20NDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Praful%20Patel%2C%20a%20key%20leader%20from%20Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20faction%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20came%20here%20without%20asking%20for%20any%20appointment.%20We%20understood%20Sharad%20Pawar%20reached%20here%20for%20a%20meeting%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20all%20came%20here%20to%20take%20his%20blessings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fajit-pawar-other-maharashtra-ncp-ministers-meet-sharad-pawar-in-mumbai%2Farticle67086781.ece%5C%22%3Ecalled%20on%3C%2Fa%3E%20Pawar%20Senior%20on%20Sunday%2C%20which%20both%20sides%20described%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimpromptu%E2%80%9D%20meeting.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20Pawars%20after%20Pawar%20Junior%20walked%20away%20with%20NCP%20MLAs%20to%20join%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20government.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20had%20said%20he%20sought%20the%20blessings%20of%20his%20uncle%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20guide%20the%20party.%20However%2C%20Pawar%20Senior%20had%20reportedly%20remained%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20on%20Monday%2C%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20Praful%20Patel%2C%20the%20MLAs%20from%20the%20breakaway%20faction%20reportedly%20urged%20Sharad%20Pawar%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20party%20remained%20united%20under%20his%20leadership.%20According%20to%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%2C%20the%20second%20meeting%20happened%20because%20several%20MLAs%20from%20Ajit%E2%80%99s%20faction%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20meet%20Pawar%20Senior%20on%20Sunday%20as%20they%20were%20away%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20in%20their%20respective%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20today%E2%80%99s%20%5BMonday%E2%80%99s%5D%20meeting%20with%20Sharad%20%3Ci%3ESaheb%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20we%20again%20asked%20him%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20NCP%20stays%20united.%20Although%20he%20attentively%20listened%20to%20us%2C%20like%20yesterday%2C%20even%20today%2C%20he%20refrained%20from%20offering%20a%20reaction%2C%E2%80%9D%20Patel%20said%20following%20a%20half-hour%20meeting%20with%20Pawar%20Senior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20leader%20from%20Sharad%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20camp%20said%20that%20Pawar%20Junior%20and%20Patel%20discussed%20disqualification%20notices%20moved%20by%20the%20former%E2%80%99s%20camp%20against%20nine%20NCP%20MLAs%20who%20joined%20the%20Shinde%20government.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20they%20also%20urged%20Sharad%20Pawar%20to%20join%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20surprise%20visit%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20faction%2C%20NCP%20state%20president%20Jayant%20Patil%2C%20a%20loyalist%20of%20Pawar%20Senior%2C%20who%20was%20at%20his%20residence%20after%20having%20met%20with%20governor%20Ramesh%20Bais%2C%20hurried%20to%20the%20Chavan%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20informed%20about%20their%20arrival%20and%20asked%20to%20reach%20the%20Chavan%20Centre%20without%20delay.%20Pawar%20%3Ci%3ESaheb%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0told%20me%20that%20he%20would%20only%20meet%20them%20in%20my%20presence.%20During%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20