Idea%20Help%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Underprivileged%20Kids%20Access%20Free%20Tutors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETen-year-old%20Prince%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20excitement%20is%20unmissable%20as%20the%20clock%20strikes%202%20pm%2C%20signalling%20the%20end%20of%20the%20school%20day%20at%20SDMC%20Pratibha%20Vidyalaya%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Defence%20Colony.%20His%20favourite%20part%20of%20the%20day%20is%20just%20about%20to%20begin%20%E2%80%94%20the%20after-school%20maths%20lesson.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20fuels%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F293875%2Fworlds-first-braille-literacy-award-winning-device-annie-innovation-for-blind-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove%20for%20a%20subject%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20is%20often%20dreaded%20by%20most%20of%20his%20classmates%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrince%20says%20his%20mentor%20Savya%20Mittal%20is%20the%20reason%20behind%20making%20these%20classes%20%E2%80%9Cexciting%20and%20fun%E2%80%9D.%20Savya%20is%20one%20of%20the%20100%20student%20volunteers%20who%20has%20registered%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Volunteers%20for%20MCD%20Schools%E2%80%99%20mobile%20app%2C%20an%20initiative%20by%20Delhi%20resident%20Anant%20Bagrodia%2C%20who%20himself%20is%20a%20student%20in%20Class%2012%20at%20the%20Vasant%20Valley%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Prince%20is%20in%20awe%20of%20how%20Math%20can%20be%20simplified%20to%20such%20a%20degree%2C%20Savya%2C%20too%2C%20thoroughly%20enjoys%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F182719%2Fteacher-lives-in-forests-for-20-years-uplifts-one-of-keralas-most-underprivileged-tribes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprocess%20of%20teaching%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20the%20two%20spread%20out%20their%20notes%2C%20ready%20for%20another%20class%20of%20learning%20mixed%20with%20fun%2C%20Anant%20says%20this%20was%20exactly%20the%20motive%20with%20which%20he%20launched%20the%20mobile%20app.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20all%20started%20as%20a%20passion%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20decision%20to%20tutor%20kids%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2016-year-old%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20thick%20of%20his%20own%20studies%20and%20extracurriculars%2C%20thinks%20back%20to%20when%20an%20anecdote%20shared%20by%20his%20mother%20ended%20up%20shaping%20this%20unique%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivani%2C%20Anant%E2%80%99s%20mom%20would%20dedicate%20hours%20teaching%20underprivileged%20children%20in%20MCD%20schools%20as%20part%20of%20a%20volunteering%20project.%20Some%20time%20in%20January%2C%20she%20recalled%20to%20her%20son%20how%20among%20the%20many%20children%20she%20would%20tutor%2C%20one%20child%20had%20caught%20her%20attention.%20Prince%2C%20as%20she%20later%20told%20Anant%2C%20was%20a%20bright%20child%20who%20could%20grasp%20concepts%20well%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F181572%2Fkerala-tea-seller-teacher-forest-library-edamalakkudy-amazing-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20right%20tutoring%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG-20230717-WA0010-1689597036.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22'Volunteer%20for%20MCD%20Schools'%20enables%20willing%20student%20volunteers%20to%20connect%20with%20underprivileged%20kids%20across%20Delhi%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG-20230717-WA0010-1689597036.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG-20230717-WA0010-1689597036-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20ht