2723%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Feurope-heatwave-how-is-it-impacting-spain-italy-and-the-continents-other-most-popular-holiday-destinations-12922373%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meteorologists%20are%20warning%20temperatures%20will%20hit%20new%20record%20highs%20across%20southern%20Europe%20this%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A693%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Feurope-heatwave-how-is-it-impacting-spain-italy-and-the-continents-other-most-popular-holiday-destinations-12922373%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Feurope-heatwave-how-is-it-impacting-spain-italy-and-the-continents-other-most-popular-holiday-destinations-12922373%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Feurope-heatwave-how-is-it-impacting-spain-italy-and-the-continents-other-most-popular-holiday-destinations-12922373%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Compensation%20for%20Accident%20Victims%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20%E2%80%98Favour%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20State%20Must%20Be%20More%20Accountable%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F04044756%2FFxswnLFaIAEMPBf.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20of%20our%20fellow%20citizens%20by%20accident%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20routine.%20Turning%20the%20daily%20newspaper%20to%20the%20city%20pages%20inevitably%20brings%20news%20of%20deaths%20from%20accidents%20of%20various%20kinds%20%E2%80%93%20a%20stray%20bike%20rider%20here%2C%20a%20lone%20bicyclist%20there%2C%20two%20people%20sleeping%20on%20the%20pavement%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20Every%20so%20often%2C%20reports%20of%20accidents%20that%20have%20a%20higher%20count%20of%20casualties%20make%20it%20to%20the%20front%20pages%2C%20sometimes%20as%20the%20lead%20story.%20These%20describe%20a%20bus%20falling%20into%20a%20gorge%20or%20catching%20fire%2C%20a%20train%20smashing%20into%20another%2C%20and%20on%20occasion%2C%20a%20boat%20overturning.%20Other%20forms%20of%20accidents%20%E2%80%93%20bridge%20or%20building%20collapses%2C%20stampedes%2C%20fires%20and%20such%20%E2%80%93%20are%20rarer%2C%20but%20still%20feature%20multiple%20times%20a%20year.%20In%20India%2C%20there%20is%20no%20end%20to%20the%20news%20of%20accidental%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20familiar%20story%20emerges%20after%20the%20accident.%20The%20state%20chief%20minister%20announces%20ex%20gratia%20compensation%20to%20the%20next%20of%20kin%20of%20those%20dead%20and%20for%20the%20injured.%20For%20train%20accidents%2C%20the%20railway%20minister%20also%20announces%20compensation.%20The%20prime%20minister%20loosens%20purse%20strings%20and%20adds%20to%20the%20money%20announced%20for%20the%20next%20of%20kin%20of%20accident%20victims.%20Monetary%20compensation%20and%20treatment%20are%20also%20promised%20for%20those%20injured.%20The%20Latin-origin%20terms%20%E2%80%9Cex%20gratia%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Csolatium%E2%80%9D%20are%20seen%20only%20in%20such%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20%E2%80%9Cex%20gratia%E2%80%9D%20compensation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Oxford%20dictionary%20defines%20ex%20gratia%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20payment%20made%20as%20a%20favour%20or%20from%20a%20sense%20of%20moral%20obligation%20rather%20than%20because%20of%20any%20legal%20requirement%E2%80%9D.%20Read%20that%20again%2C%20slowly%20and%20carefully.%20Why%20would%20our%20governments%20be%20paying%20accident%20victims%20as%20a%20favour%3F%20What%20place%20does%20a%20sense%20of%20moral%20obligation%20have%20in%20a%20democracy%20where%20we%20are%20not%20ruled%20by%20kings%2C%20benevolent%20or%20otherwise%2C%20but%20elect%20our%20representatives%20and%20have%20processes%20that%20make%20our%20government%20answerable%20to%20us%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20the%20sin%20of%20repeated%20and%20frequent%20failure%20of%20governments%20in%20ensuring%20safety%20washed%20away%20because%20it%20feels%20morally%20obliged%20to%20compensate%20the%20victims%3F%20And%20is%20the%20ex%20gratia%20fair%20and%20adequate%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernments%20pays%20woefully%20inadequate%20amounts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20tragic%20accident%20occurs%20and%20the%20government%20rushes%20in%20with%20immediate%20ex%20gratia%20relief%2C%20it%20can%20be%20tempting%20to%20interpret%20positively%20the%20urgent%20compensation%20to%20the%20aggrieved%2C%20that%20too%20from%20a%20State%20that%20usually%20imposes%20significant%20delays%20for%20money%20it%20owes%20citizens.%20This%20temptation%20must%20be%20resisted%2C%20because%20ex%20gratia%20is%20arbitrary%2C%20inadequate%20and%20seldom%20well-administered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20announced%20an%20ex%20gratia%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20to%20the%20kin%20of%20the%2041%20people%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F41-kumbh-pilgrims-killed-in-stampede%2Farticleshow%2F149362.cms%5C%22%3EKumbh%20Mela%3C%2Fa%3E%20stampede%20in%20Nashik.%20Nearly%2020%20years%20later%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20announced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.abplive.com%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Fandhra-pradesh-tdp-announces-rs-24-lakh-ex-gratia-for-kin-of-deceased-in-nellore-stampede-1572487%5C%22%3Esame%20amount%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20the%20kin%20of%20those%20who%20died%20in%20a%20stampede%20at%20a%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20roadshow%20in%20Nellore%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(the%20Union%20government%20additionally%20announced%20Rs%202%20lakh%20per%20victim).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20performed%20online%20searches%20to%20determine%20if%20there%20were%20patterns%20to%20the%20promised%20amount%20of%20ex%20gratia%20compensation%20across%20the%20country.%20In%20almost%20every%20state%2C%20the%20amounts%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20frozen%20at%20some%20point%20in%20time%20and%20not%20revised%20for%20multiple%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F7wWQR%2F2%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5B%20Insert%20title%20here%20%5D%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22746%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20chief%20ministers%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20have%20been%20consistent%20in%20announcing%20a%20sum%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20incident%20type.%20The%20Mantralaya%20fire%20of%202012%20in%20Maharashtra%20claimed%20five%20lives%3B%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%20announced%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20as%20compensation.%20For%20each%20of%20the%2020%2B%20accidents%20in%20Maharashtra%20from%202013%20onwards%20that%20we%20were%20able%20to%20document%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20(irrespective%20of%20the%20ruling%20party)%20announced%20Rs%205%20lakh%20ex%20gratia%20to%20the%20next%20of%20kin%20of%20those%20who%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Tamil%20Nadu%20over%20the%20same%20period%2C%20the%20ex%20gratia%20from%20the%20chief%20minister%20ranged%20between%20Rs%202%20lakh%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20over%2030%2B%20incidents%2C%20with%20two%20exceptions%20%E2%80%93%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20announced%20for%20the%2017%20deceased%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnavjeevanexpress.com%2Fmettupalayam-wall-collapse-victims-kin-to-get-rs-10-lakh-ex-gratia%2F%5C%22%3Ewall%20collapse%20in%20Mettupalayam%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20December%202018%20and%20for%20three%20school%20students%20who%20died%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Ftamil-nadu-thirunelveli-students-killed-wall-collapse-school-1888864-2021-12-17%5C%22%3Ewall%20collapse%20in%20in%20Thirunelveli%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%202021.%20A%20smaller%20sample%20of%20~3-5%20accidents%20each%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20West%20Bengal%20failed%20to%20turn%20up%20compensation%20more%20than%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20except%20for%20incidents%20involving%20the%20armed%20forces%20or%20industrial%20accidents%20(gas%20leaks%20in%20Vishakhapatnam%20and%20Ludhiana).%20For%20larger%20incidents%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20stepped%20in%20with%20an%20additional%20compensation%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh.%20All%20of%20these%20are%20less%20than%20the%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20insurance%20cover%20that%20passengers%20can%20buy%20when%20purchasing%20a%20train%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20current%20minimum%20wage%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftradingeconomics.com%2Findia%2Fminimum-wages%5C%22%3ERs%20178%20per%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20person%20that%20works%2025%20days%20in%20a%20month%20would%20earn%20Rs.%2053%2C400%20a%20year.%20For%20contrast%2C%20note%20that%20the%20benefits%20under%20reservation%20for%20economically%20weaker%20sections%20(EWSs)%20of%20society%20are%20for%20persons%20whose%20family%20has%20gross%20annual%20income%20below%20Rs%208%20lakh!%20The%20default%20compensation%20range%20of%20Rs%202-5%20lakh%20barely%20represents%20a%20few%20years%20of%20minimum%20wage%20work%2C%20let%20alone%20accounting%20for%20the%20productive%20capacities%20of%20those%20who%20lose%20their%20lives%2C%20or%20take%20into%20account%20the%20family%20circumstances%20where%20the%20deceased%20may%20be%20a%20primary%20wage%20earner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20sound%20basis%20for%20amount%20paid%20under%20ex%20gratia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20time%20an%20accident%20occurs%2C%20the%20ruling%20establishment%20of%20the%20state%20as%20represented%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20or%20another%20minister%20unfailingly%20expresses%20deep%20grief%20and%20declares%20ex%20gratia%20as%20a%20measure%20of%20relief.%20Yet%2C%20no%20critical%20thinking%20or%20evaluation%20of%20individual%20circumstances%20is%20ever%20performed.%20The%20state%20government%20simply%20pays%20a%20pre-set%20amount%20of%20compensation%20for%20almost%20all%20incidents%2C%20as%20if%20the%20state%20bureaucracy%20follows%20a%20set%20procedure%2C%20with%20a%20hardcoded%20compensation%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscripbox.com%2Fplan%2Finflation-calculator%2F%5C%22%3Esimple%20inflation%20calculation%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20that%20to%20have%20the%20same%20purchasing%20power%20as%20Rs%205%20lakh%20in%202013%2C%20one%20would%20need%20to%20spend%20Rs.%209.51%20lakh%20as%20of%202023%3B%20yet%2C%20the%20governments%20have%20not%20made%20any%20adjustments%20to%20the%20compensation%20amounts%20over%20the%20last%20several%20years.%20It%20is%20as%20if%20the%20machinery%20that%20extends%20favours%20is%20choosing%20to%20ignore%20the%20phenomenon%20of%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20arbitrariness%20in%20the%20compensation%20announced%20%E2%80%93%20different%20states%20have%20different%20standards%2C%20and%20the%20same%20state%20promises%20different%20amounts%20seemingly%20based%20on%20the%20size%20of%20headline%20or%20the%20%3Cem%3Esuggestion%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20a%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20June%202023%20train%20accident%20in%20Balasore%20had%20victims%20that%20belonged%20to%20different%20states.%20While%20Indian%20Railways%20announced%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20the%20families%20of%20those%20deceased%2C%20each%20state%20followed%20its%20own%20default%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fodisha-train-tragedy-cm-announces-5-lakh-ex-gratia-to-kin-of-those-from-state-killed-in-accident%2Farticle66930179.ece%5C%22%3EOdisha%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fbengal-cm-distributes-ex-gratia-appointment-letters-to-kin-of-odisha-train-accident-victims%2Farticle66943026.ece%5C%22%3EBengal%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fpatna%2Fkin-of-balasore-t