ent%20contributions%20to%20the%20family)%20of%20the%20deceased%20so%20that%20the%20accident%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20up%20leading%20to%20economic%20devastation%20for%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20legitimate%20and%20accepted%20ways%20to%20determine%20this%20amount.%20Economists%20have%20standard%20models%20that%20forecast%20future%20earnings.%20Historical%20wage%20trends%20for%20different%20professions%20can%20be%20input%20into%20these%20models.%20Individual%20circumstances%20such%20as%20age%2C%20education%2C%20profession%2C%20family%20circumstances%2C%20etc.%20can%20be%20taken%20into%20account.%20Using%20a%20consistent%20and%20transparent%20methodology%20can%20produce%20reliable%20estimates%20that%20reduce%20discrimination%2C%20although%20admittedly%20this%20can%20never%20be%20perfect.%20This%20is%20the%20standard%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20accident%20victims%20can%20bring%20tort%20claims%20(%E2%80%9Ctortious%20interference%E2%80%9D)%20against%20parties%20that%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20accident.%20Courts%20and%20arbitrators%20then%20rely%20on%20economists%20to%20determine%20the%20compensation%20that%20is%20to%20be%20paid.%20These%20amounts%20will%20inevitably%20be%20higher%20than%20the%20pre-set%20%E2%80%9Cfavour%E2%80%9D%20the%20government%20extends%20through%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEx%20gratia%20compensation%20serves%20to%20absolve%20governments%20of%20their%20responsibilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inability%20to%20bring%20tort%20claims%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20class-action%20litigation%20(where%20victims%20in%20the%20same%20circumstance%20can%20bring%20a%20case%20as%20a%20group)%20in%20India%20simply%20serves%20to%20exempt%20the%20government%20and%20its%20arms%20(the%20Indian%20Railways%2C%20state%20transport%20corporations%2C%20road%20transport%20officers%20that%20issue%20vehicle%20and%20driving%20permits%2C%20factory%20and%20building%20inspectors%2C%20etc.)%20from%20being%20charged%20with%20neglect%20that%20leads%20to%20accidents.%20In%20the%20Balasore%20case%2C%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Railway%20Safety%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbalasore-accident-crs-probe-faults-signalling-traffic-ops-station-staff-8694951%2F%5C%22%3Eheld%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20signalling%20and%20operations%20staff%20jointly%20responsible.%20While%20the%20axe%20may%20fall%20on%20individual%20staff%20members%2C%20systemic%20issues%20remain%20unaddressed%20%E2%80%93%20as%20of%20June%202023%2C%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fabout-274-lakh-posts-vacant-in-indian-railways-over-17-lakh-in-safety-category-rti%2Farticle67019529.ece%5C%22%3E1.78%20lakh%20posts%20unfilled%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20safety%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20even%20when%20claims%20are%20brought%20under%20other%20laws%2C%20the%20delays%20and%20costs%20of%20our%20court%20systems%20deter%20all%20but%20the%20most%20dogged%20of%20victims%20from%20bringing%20lawsuits.%20The%20story%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20industrial%20disaster%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Bhopal%20gas%20leak%2C%20the%20inadequate%20compensation%2C%20and%20the%20futile%20multi-decade%20litigation%20%E2%80%93%20is%20illustrative%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForcing%20transport%20operators%2C%20temple%20trusts%2C%20building%20contractors%20and%20other%20entities%2C%20whether%20government%20or%20privately%20controlled%2C%20to%20pay%20out%20damages%20that%20reflect%20the%20future%20economic%20contributions%20of%20the%20deceased%20and%20injured%2C%20with%20added%20penalties%20for%20faults%20in%20implementing%20safety%20protocols%2C%20designing%20for%20safety%2C%20etc.%20creates%20incentives%20for%20improving%20safety%20standards.%20Unless%20this%20is%20done%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20continue%20to%20see%20accidents%20happen%2C%20grief%20expressed%20by%20governments%2C%20inadequate%20compensation%20announced%2C%20and%20no%20actual%20action%20to%20prevent%20accidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFavours%20are%20arbitrary%2C%20to%20be%20issued%20as%20and%20when%20a%20ruler%20pleases.%20They%20have%20no%20place%20in%20a%20modern%20democracy.%20We%20must%20demand%20accountability%20and%20action%20from%20our%20elected%20representatives%20to%20make%20compensation%20a%20reality%20and%20create%20incentives%20to%20fix%20for%20improving%20safety%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMegha%20Kajale%20is%20a%20student%20at%20the%20Gokhale%20Institute%20of%20Politics%20and%20Economics%20and%20Mihir%20Mahajan%20is%20adjunct%20fellow%2C%20Takshashila%20Institution.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689597028000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F04044756%2FFxswnLFaIAEMPBf.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcompensation-for-accident-victims-isnt-a-favour-and-the-state-must-be-more-accountable%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22State%20governments%20determine%20ex%20gratia%20compensation%20in%20arbitrary%20ways%20%E2%80%93%20and%20use%20this%20as%20a%20way%20to%20get%20out%20of%20any%20further%20legal%20or%20moral%20obligations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcompensation-for-accident-victims-isnt-a-favour-and-the-state-must-be-more-accountable%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zee%20constitutes%20interim%20panel%20following%20Sebi's%20bar%20on%20Goenka%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689596485000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-10%2F07%2Ffull%2F1633611047-9186.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fzee-entertainment-constitutes-interim-panel-following-sebi-s-bar-on-goenka-123