162218%2FUntitled-design-5-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EBritish-French%20actress%C2%A0and%20singer%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fjane-birkin-at-75-pop-icon-par-excellence%2Fa-60095573%5C%22%3EJane%20Birkin%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20passed%20away%C2%A0in%20Paris%20at%20the%20age%20of%2076%2C%20the%20French%20Culture%20Ministry%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20London-born%20entertainer%C2%A0suffered%20from%20health%20problems%20in%20recent%20years%20that%20forced%20her%20to%20cancel%20concerts.%20She%20had%20a%20mild%20stroke%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBirkin%20first%20became%20famous%20internationally%20in%201969%20when%20she%20and%20her%20lover%2C%20the%20late%20French%20musician%20Serge%20Gainsbourg%2C%20sang%20the%20controversial%20hit%20song%20%E2%80%98Je%20T%E2%80%99aime%E2%80%A6%20Moi%20Non%20Plus%E2%80%99%20with%20sexually%20explicit%20lyrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20love%20in%20Paris%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJane%20Mallory%20Birkin%20was%20born%20in%20London%20in%20December%201946.%20Her%20mother%20was%20an%20actress%20Judy%20Campbell%20and%C2%A0her%20father%20a%20naval%20officer%20David%20Birkin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20first%20marriage%20came%20at%2017%2C%20when%20Birkin%20married%20composer%20John%20Barry%2C%20himself%20famous%20for%20composing%20the%20iconic%20%E2%80%98James%20Bond%E2%80%99%20theme.%20Birkin%20and%20Barry%20had%20a%20daughter%2C%20Kate%2C%20but%20their%20marriage%20fell%20apart%20after%20only%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201966%2C%20Birkin%20appeared%20nude%20in%20Michelangelo%20Antonioni%E2%80%99s%20film%20%3Cem%3EBlow-Up%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20part%20of%20a%20threesome%20sex%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20on%20a%20set%20of%20a%20romantic%20comedy%20in%20Paris%2C%20she%20met%20French%20singer%20and%20songwriter%20Serge%20Gainsbourg.%20Although%C2%A0Gainsbourg%20was%2018%20years%20older%2C%20the%20two%20started%20a%2013-year-long%20relationship%20that%20prompted%20Birkin%20to%20permanently%20move%20to%20Paris%20and%20eventually%20made%20them%C2%A0France%E2%80%99s%20most%20famous%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20also%20had%20a%20daughter%2C%20Charlotte%2C%20who%20has%20become%20a%20successful%20actress%20and%20singer%20in%20her%20own%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoving%20away%20from%C2%A0Gainsbourg%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBirkin%20built%C2%A0her%20career%20and%20image%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20forming%20an%20iconic%20look%20which%20include%20flared%20jeans%2C%C2%A0mini%20dresses%20and%20messy%20bangs.%20In%201980%2C%20she%20left%C2%A0Gainsbourg%C2%A0to%20focus%20on%20her%20movie%20career%2C%20which%20also%20included%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffrom-sexy-singer-to-film-star-jane-birkin-at-70%2Fa-36748398%5C%22%3Eart%20house%20productions%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20many%20of%20France%E2%80%99s%20leading%20directors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Birkin%20and%C2%A0Gainsbourg%20continued%20to%20cooperate%20professionally%2C%20with%C2%A0Gainsbourg%20writing%20songs%20for%20her%20after%20their%20split.%20The%20songwriter%2C%20who%20struggled%20with%20alcoholism%2C%20died%C2%A0of%20a%20heart%20attack%20in%201991%20at%C2%A0%20the%20age%20of%C2%A062.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBirkin%20continued%20to%20pursue%20her%20music%20career%20after%20Gainsbourg%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20releasing%20%E2%80%98A%20la%20Legere%E2%80%99%20in%201998%2C%20writing%20the%20album%20%E2%80%98Arabesque%E2%80%99%20in%202002%20and%20publishing%20a%20collection%20of%20live%20recordings%2C%20%E2%80%98Jane%20at%20the%20Palace%E2%80%99%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBag%20named%20%E2%80%98Birkin%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actress%20also%20left%20her%20mark%20in%20the%20world%20of%20fashion.%20In%201984%2C%20French%20luxury%20label%20Hermes%20named%20one%20of%20its%20handbags%20after%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20said%20that%20in%201981%20Birkin%20was%20on%20a%20flight%20next%20to%20the%20late%20Jean-Louise%20Dumas%2C%20then%20CEO%20of%20Hermes.%20Birkin%20had%20tried%20to%20put%20her%20luggage%20in%20the%20overhead%20compartment%20and%20famously%20complained%20that%20she%20had%20yet%20to%20find%20a%20purse%20big%20enough%20to%20hold%20all%20of%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20belongings.%20This%20prompted%20Dumas%20to%20prototype%20a%20bag%20that%20would%20become%20the%20iconic%20Birkin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fjane-birkin-wants-name-change-for-namesake-hermes-bags%2Fa-18615214%5C%22%3EBirkin%20asked%20Hermes%20to%20drop%20her%20name%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20bag%20after%20animal%20rights%20group%20People%20for%20the%20Ethical%20Treatment%20of%20Animals%C2%A0alerted%20her%20to%20the%20cruel%20farming%20practices%20of%20crocodiles%20for%20their%20leather.%20She%20later%20relented%20after%20Hermes%20investigated%20the%20practices%20and%20found%20them%20to%20be%20an%20%E2%80%9Cisolated%20irregularity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Factress-and-singer-jane-birkin-dies-aged-76%2Fa-66247387%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689592114000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17162218%2FUntitled-design-5-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Factor-singer-jane-birkin-dies-aged-76%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Birkin%20first%20became%20famous%20internationally%20in%201969%20when%20she%20and%20her%20lover%2C%20the%20late%20French%20musician%20Serge%20Gainsbourg%2C%20sang%20the%20controversial%20hit%20song%20'Je%20T'aime...%20Moi%20Non%20Plus'%20with%20sexually%20explicit%20lyrics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Factor-singer-jane-birkin-dies-aged-76%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20'We%20Give%20PM%20Modi%2010%20Days%20to%20Come%20to%20Manipur%20to%20Help%20Resolve%20the%20Conflict%2C%20It%20Is%20His%20Duty%20to%20Do%20So'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17162955%2FKT-17-July.00_35_18_06.Still002.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20becomes%20increasingly%20clear%20that%20the%20government%2C%20both%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Imphal%2C%20is%20incapable%20of%20handling%20the%20crisis%20in%20Manipur%20effectively%20%E2%80%93%20and%20some%20would%20even%20add%20sincerely%20%E2%80%93%20civil%20society%20organisations%20are%20increasingly%20stepping%20into%20the%20picture.%20One%20such%20organisation%20is%20the%20Forum%20for%20Restoration%20of%20Peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreated%20as%20a%20direct%20response%20to%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%20that%20started%20on%20May%203%2C%20the%20Forum%E2%80%99s%20convenor%2C%20Ashang%20Kasar%2C%20has%20said%20the%20two%20immediate%20necessary%20steps%20to%20restore%20peace%20and%20harmony%20are%20the%20replacement%20of%20Biren%20Singh%20as%20chief%20minister%20(but%20not%20necessarily%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule)%20and%20an%20initiative%20directly%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20start%20a%20dialogue%20between%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20communities.%20If%20these%20steps%20are%20not%20taken%2C%20Kasar%20said%2C%20the%20situation%20will%20markedly%20deteriorate%20and%20the%20responsibility%20and%20blame%20will%20then%20lie%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20and%2C%20specifically%2C%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2014%2C%20the%20Forum%20wrote%20directly%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20asking%20him%20to%20visit%20Manipur%20within%2010%20days%2C%20and%20take%20an%20initiative%20to%20bring%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20together.%20Kasar%20said%20he%E2%80%99s%20had%20no%20response%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20to%20his%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Forum%E2%80%99s%20letter%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20case%20Your%20Honour%20fails%20to%20come%20to%20Manipur%20and%20resolve%20the%20conflict%20within%20ten%20days%2C%20this%20Forum%20would%20be%20compelled%20to%20resort%20to%20any%20step%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%20Kasar%20explained%20that%20though%20this%20may%20sound%20like%20a%20threat%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20intended%20as%20an%20expression%20of%20the%20Forum%E2%80%99s%20anguish%20and%20desperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FYYUOBTqkHkM%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKasar%20said%20if%20the%20prime%20minister%20fails%20to%20come%20by%20the%20end%20of%2010%20days%20(which%20is%20July%2024%2F25)%2C%20the%20Forum%20will%20organise%20%E2%80%9Ca%20massive%20people%E2%80%99s%20movement%E2%80%9D%20in%20Manipur.%20To%20quote%20from%20its%20press%20release%20of%20July%203%20the%20Forum%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Forum%20for%20Restoration%20of%20Peace%20%E2%80%A6%20will%20demonstrate%20a%20massive%20people%E2%80%99s%20movement%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20of%20India%20to%20show%20before%20the%20world%20that%20the%20Union%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20not%20interested%20to%20resolve%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20initiative%20by%20the%20Forum%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20first%20killing%20of%20a%20Naga%20person%20has%20taken%20place%20in%20Imphal.%20Both%20the%20United%20Naga%20Council%20and%20the%20All%20Naga%20Students%20Association%20have%20issued%20strongly-worded%20press%20releases%20demanding%20a%20judicial%20inquiry%20and%20action%20against%20Meitei%20Meira%20Paibis%20women%20%E2%80%9Cwho%20are%20complicit%20in%20this%20act%20of%20crime%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nagas%20are%2024%25%20of%20the%20population%20of%20Manipur%20and%20so%20far%20they%20have%20not%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20Kuki-Meitei%20clashes.%20This%20is%20why%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Naga%20woman%20on%20Saturday%20(July%2015)%20is%20significant%20as%20is%20the%20allegation%20made%20by%20the%20Nagas%20that%20Meitei%20Meira%20Paibis%20women%20are%20involved.%20Many%20believe%20it%20could%20be%20an%20attempt%20to%20escalate%20the%20Manipur%20communal%20clash%20to%20involve%20the%20Naga%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Kasar%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Indigenous%20People%E2%80%99s%20Forum%20of%20Manipur%2C%20criticised%20the%20strategy%20so%20far%20adopted%20by%20the%20central%20government%20to%20tackle%20the%20crisis%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20he%20spoke%20about%20the%20peace%20committee%20created%20by%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20Kasar%20said%20he%20was%20the%20person%20who%20proposed%20the%20committee%20and%20whilst%20he%20is%20grateful%20that%20Shah%20accepted%20his%20proposal%20and%20acted%20on%20it%2C%20the%20committee%20that%E2%80%99s%20been%20created%20serves%20no%20purpose.%20There%20are%20three%20things%20wrong%20with%20it.%20First%2C%20it%20should%20have%20included%20all%20the%2034%20tribes%20of%20Manipur%20but%20involves%20barely%20two%20or%20three.%20Second%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20other%20ministers%20of%20the%20government%20should%20not%20be%20involved%20because%20in%20Kuki%20eyes%20they%20are%20distrusted%20and%20disliked.%20Furthermore%2C%20many%20of%20these%20politicians%20failed%20to%20act%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20violence%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20have%20no%20role%20in%20a%20peace%20committee.%20Third%2C%20the%20peace%20committee%20should%20not%20involve%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis%20at%20this%20stage%20because%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Cwarring%20communities%E2%80%9D.%20With%20their%20involvement%20the%20committee%20cannot%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKasar%20was%20particularly%20critical%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20for%20handling%20Manipur.%20He%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CPumping%20in%20thousands%20and%20thousands%20of%20military%20personnel%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20will%20not%20bring%20peace%20and%20normalcy.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20should%20have%20invited%20both%20the%20parties%20on%20his%20small%20table%20and%20resolve%20the%20issue%20amicably.%E2%80%9D%20His%20conclusion%20is%20that%20a%20dialogue%20is%20needed.%20Sending%20in%2060%2C000%20soldiers%20is%20not%20the%20right%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Kasar%20was%20sharply%20critical%20of%20the%20Manipur%20governor.%20He%20said%20she%20was%20not%20just%20new%20to%20the%20job%20but%20inexperienced%20and%20ill-advised.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThe%20Governor%20of%20Manipur%20is%20only%20focusing%20attention%20towards%20the%20valley%20civil%20society%20organisations%20leaving%20behind%20%E2%80%A6%20civil%20society%20organisations%20of%20all%20communities%20in%20the%20hills.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20appeal%20the%20Governor%20of%20Manipur%20to%20convene%20a%20meeting%20of%20all%20civil%20society%20organisations%20of%20Manipur%20of%20both%20the%20hills%20and%20the%20valley%20to%20discuss%20and%20seek%20more%20views%20and%20opinions%20on%20the%20prevailing%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Kasar%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Forum%20for%20Restoration%20of%20Peace%20does%20not%20support%20the%20Kuki%20demand%20for%20separate%20statehood.%20He%20added%20it%20cannot%20be%20considered%20%E2%80%9Cat%20all%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Kasar%20said%20the%20Meitei%20demand%20for%20scheduled%20tribe%20status%20cannot%20be%20part%20of%20any%20negotiations%20that%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis%20have.%20He%20said%20it%20must%20be%20left%20to%20the%20courts%20to%20resolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689592057000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17162955%2FKT-17-July.00_35_18_06.Still002.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fwatch-we-give-pm-modi-10-days-to-come-to-manipur-to-help-resolve-the-conflict-it-is-his-duty-to-do-so%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ashang%20Kasar%20has%20said%20the%20two%20immediate%20necessary%20steps%20to%20restore%20peace%20and%20harmony%20in%20Manipur%20are%20the%20replacement%20of%20Biren%20Singh%20as%20chief%20minister%20(but%20not%20necessarily%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule)%20and%20an%20initiative%20directly%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20start%20a%20dialogue%20between%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20communities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A108%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fwatch-we-give-pm-modi-10-days-to-come-to-manipur-to-help-resolve-the-conflict-it-is-his-duty-to-do-so%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Afghan%20Singer%20Hasiba%20Noori%20Killed%20in%20Attack%20by%20Unknown%20Gunmen%20in%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F17103237%2FUntitled-design-5.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hasiba%20Noori%2C%20a%20well-known%20female%20singer%20from%20Afghanistan%20who%20had%20sought%20refuge%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20an%20attack%20by%20unidentified%20assailants%20in%20the%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20province%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famu.tv%2F56737%2F%5C%22%3EAmu%20TV%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20motive%20behind%20the%20attack%20remains%20unclear%2C%20prompting%20the%20initiation%20of%20an%20investig