ions%20to%20indigenously%20grown%20fruits.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Digvijay%20Singh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Digvijay%20got%20his%20first%20order%20of%201%2C000%20chocolates%20from%20a%20car%20showroom%20owner.%20He%20also%20launched%20his%20brand%20under%20the%20name%20Saraam%20the%20same%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20happy%20beyond%20words%20and%20was%20very%20excited%20for%20the%20future%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20hobby%20to%20kill%20time%20has%20today%20become%20a%20successful%20chocolate%20brand%20that%20has%20made%20a%20lifetime%20revenue%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20and%20sold%20over%202%20tonnes%20of%20chocolate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20Indian%20fruits%20to%20the%20limelight%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Digvijay%20came%20across%20an%20article%20online%20on%20how%20there%20were%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20indigenous%20fruits%20that%20were%20being%20extinct.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20mentions%20of%20fruits%20that%20I%20have%20never%20even%20heard%20about%20and%20I%20was%20very%20shocked.%20For%20us%20fruits%20mostly%20mean%20the%20mainstream%20apples%2C%20mangoes%2C%20bananas%20and%20grapes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHearing%20about%20how%20so%20many%20tasty%20fruits%20are%20left%20ignored%20was%20sad%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it.%20This%20is%20when%20the%20idea%20of%20putting%20them%20in%20chocolate%20came%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigvijay%20researched%20indigenously%20grown%20fruits%20such%20as%20kokam%2C%20ice%20apple%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%20and%20tried%20them%20to%20discover%20which%20ones%20go%20well%20with%20chocolate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20culinary%20world%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20beyond%20exotic%20berries%2C%20cherries%20and%20oranges.%20I%20have%20never