efore%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20lived%20in%20Maharashtra%20my%20whole%20life%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20see%20so%20many%20snacks%20that%20nobody%20knew%20about.%20Additionally%2C%20all%20these%20were%20handmade%20and%20without%20preservatives.%20Those%20women%20also%20told%20me%20how%20they%20do%20not%20have%20much%20employment%20and%20were%20constantly%20under%20financial%20stress%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20conversations%20with%20the%20women%20gave%20the%20duo%20the%20idea%20of%20starting%20a%20company%20that%20could%20bridge%20this%20gap.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20%E2%80%98Why%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%20create%20a%20marketplace%20and%20supply%20chain%20for%20these%20women%3F%E2%80%99%20and%20then%20in%20September%202021%2C%20Aazol%20was%20born%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-5-1688737718.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22women%20from%20remote%20village%20in%20Maharashtra%20working%20for%20Aazol%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-5-1688737718.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-5-1688737718-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-5-1688737718-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-5-1688737718-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-5-1688737718-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323132%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EApurva%20left%20her%20three%20decades%20of%20corporate%20career%20to%20work%20in%20the%20social%