%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheetalakshmi%2C%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20school%2C%20believes%20that%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20bring%20the%20concept%20of%20sustainability%20to%20life.%20%E2%80%9CA%20sustainable%20world%2C%20filled%20with%20the%20blessings%20and%20bounty%20of%20nature%2C%20is%20the%20best%20gift%20we%20can%20leave%20behind%20for%20future%20generations.%20At%20school%20we%20subtly%20sensitise%20students%20about%20the%20environment%20through%20hands-on%20and%20thought-provoking%20activities%2C%20by%20incorporating%20them%20into%20their%20curriculum%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20students%20have%20been%20in%20awe%20of%20the%20place%20and%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20move%20around%20freely.%20They%20are%20given%20a%20scheduled%20time%20daily%20to%20have%20outdoor%20activities%2C%20have%20classroom%20sessions%20outside%20in%20the%20SOUL%20(School%20Outdoor%20Learning%20Hubs)%2C%20climb%20trees%20if%20they%20please%2C%20and%20enjoy%20fresh%20and%20clean%20air%20and%20sunlight.%20If%20they%20are%20learning%20about%20fruit-bearing%20trees%20then%20they%20can%20see%20those%20in%20real-time%20in%20the%20school%20which%20aids%20their%20learning%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaida%2C%20a%20student%20of%20Class%208%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20school%20is%20unlike%20any%20other%20school%20in%20the%20city.%20We%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20go%20outdoors%20and%20learn%20from%20nature.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20rainwater%20harvesting%20that%20we%20learn%20in%20books%20is%20right%20here%20in%20the%20school.%20We%20also%20plant%20our%20food%20near%20our%20cafeteria%2C%20which%20gives%20us%20an%20idea%20of%20where%20our%20food%20comes%20from%20and%20the%20hard%20work%20involved%20in%20growing%20food.%20I%20love%20how%20our%20teachers%20always%20give%20us%20the%20time%20to%20explore%20the%20surroundings.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Akanksha%20and%20Saurabh%20believe%20